学”的社会组织行为也会提到相关内容，我们该如何看待？</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#4-%E6%88%91%E4%BB%AC%E8%AF%A5%E6%8A%B1%E7%9D%80%E6%80%8E%E6%A0%B7%E7%9A%84%E6%80%81%E5%BA%A6%E6%89%8D%E7%AE%97%E6%98%AF%E2%80%9C%E6%AD%A3%E7%A1%AE%E5%9C%B0%E2%80%9D%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0%E7%A4%BE%E4%BC%9A%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E5%AD%A6%EF%BC%9F\"><span class=\"toc-text\">4.我们该抱着怎样的态度才算是“正确地”学习社会工程学？</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%AF%B9%E4%BA%8E%E4%BB%BB%E4%BD%95%E7%9F%A5%E8%AF%86%E9%83%BD%E8%A6%81%E6%8A%B1%E6%9C%89%E6%95%AC%E7%95%8F%E4%B9%8B%E5%BF%83\"><span class=\"toc-text\">对于任何知识都要抱有敬畏之心</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E7%A4%BE%E4%BC%9A%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E5%AD%A6%E6%98%AF%E7%94%A8%E6%9D%A5%E5%B8%AE%E5%8A%A9%E6%88%91%E4%BB%AC%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0%E7%A4%BE%E4%BC%9A%E4%BB%B7%E5%80%BC%E7%9A%84%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%8D%E6%98%AF%E7%94%A8%E6%9D%A5%E8%83%8C%E7%A6%BB%E6%88%96%E8%80%85%E9%80%83%E8%84%B1%E7%A4%BE%E4%BC%9A%E8%AF%84%E5%88%A4%E7%9A%84\"><span class=\"toc-text\">社会工程学是用来帮助我们实现社会价值的，不是用来背离或者逃脱社会评判的</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E4%B8%8D%E8%A6%81%E8%B5%B0%E7%81%AB%E5%85%A5%E9%AD%94%EF%BC%8C%E4%BF%9D%E6%8C%81%E6%9C%AC%E5%BF%83\"><span class=\"toc-text\">不要走火入魔，保持本心</span></a></li></ol></li></ol></li></ol>","author":{"name":"Akpigs","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://img1.imgtp.com/2022/12/28/m2fD4XcB.jpg","link":"/","description":"Sharp tools make good work, 2023新年快乐！","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/akpigs","twitter":"https://twitter.com/EmilyLe443","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"https://akpigs.blog.csdn.net/","juejin":"","customs":{"discord":{"icon":"/svg/discord.svg","link":"https://discord.gg/vS7yaWgW"},"bilibili":{"icon":"/svg/bilibili.svg","link":"https://www.bilibili.com"},"facebook":{"icon":"/svg/facebook.svg","link":"https://facebook.com"}}}},"mappe